title: Railworks TS2014 BR Class 117 DMU
description:
The Class 117 DMU for Train Simulator is available in British Rail green livery and features a full three-car consist including a Driving Motor Brake Second, Driving Motor Second and Trailer Composite Lavatory, complete with passenger view, cab lighting and mechanical gear change. 

The locomotive is also Quick Drive compatible, giving you the freedom to drive the BR Class 117 on any Quick Drive enabled route for Train Simulator. Also included are scenarios specifically for the West Somerset Railway route (available separately and required to play these scenarios).




Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.




A Team tpb_4_ever upload.
